Saudi Environmental Society (SENS; Arabic: جمعية البيئة السعودية) bụ obodo Saudi tọrọ ntọala dị ka otu mba na-anaghị akwụ ụgwọ na 2006 dị ka mkpebi nke Ministry of Social Affairs No
(34770), na edebanye aha na ọrụ ebere
ndekọ n'okpuru nọmba (335) na ụbọchị nke 14/5/1427 AH
Onye isi ala Saudi Environment Society bụ Onye isi ala Turki bin Nasser.

N'okpuru mkpebi a - mkpebi ntọala - e nyela ọtụtụ ọrụ na ọha mmadụ, ọkachasị mmepe nke gburugburu ebe obibi Saudi na imeziwanye ọnọdụ ndị bi na mpaghara na mpaghara ndị nwere nsogbu gburugburu ebe obibi site n'ịrụ ọrụ n'ịmepụta mmemme mmepe na-adịgide adịgide

Na mgbakwunye na ịrụ ọrụ n'ịzụlite ọrụ afọ ofufo site n'ịmepụta nnukwu ndị ọrụ afọ ofufu na inye aka n'ịkwalite ọrụ nke ngalaba onwe iji jeere nsogbu gburugburu ebe obibi ozi na mpaghara nchedo gburugburu ebe obibi na nchekwa nke ihe okike na anụ ọhịa.
